# 2026 board election

The SPI board had 1 seat available for the 2026 board election.  The
nomination period opened on July 1st 2026 and closed on July 14th 2026.

Nominations were received from:

 * [Gordian Edenhofer](platform-gordian-edenhofer)

The following people's board terms expire with this election:

 * Joe Conway

This election is governed by resolution
[2004-08-10.dbg.2](/corporate/resolutions/2004/2004-08-10.dbg.2/)

As there were enough open seats for all confirmed candidates, and no other
voting measures to put before the members, no poll was conducted and the
candidates (1) were acclaimed.
